0:02:21.540,0:02:24.680
We wish Your Majesty good health and eternal blessings.

0:02:25.660,0:02:27.640
I haven't seen Lady Sourire for some time.

0:02:27.860,0:02:30.300
Raise your head and let me look at you.

0:02:34.980,0:02:36.300
All rise.

0:02:36.940,0:02:38.960
We thank Your Majesty.

0:02:40.820,0:02:42.840
Lady Sourire not only has good manners

0:02:43.060,0:02:45.520
but also a gentle nature.

0:02:49.900,0:02:51.880
I bow in respect before Your Majesty.

0:02:52.000,0:02:53.960
Allow me to kneel to greet Your Majesty.

0:02:53.960,0:02:55.860
I rejoice at seeing Your Majesty.

0:02:56.940,0:02:59.960
Very well. You are well-mannered indeed.

0:03:00.180,0:03:01.820
I am young and unschooled.

0:03:01.860,0:03:03.740
Blessed by Your Majesty's grace

0:03:03.820,0:03:05.900
and the teachings from Her Majesty and the other concubines,

0:03:06.280,0:03:07.840
I have not behaved improperly.

0:03:07.980,0:03:11.780
No wonder the emperor likes you. I like you, too.

0:03:12.780,0:03:14.580
-Bamboo.
-Yes.

0:03:14.580,0:03:17.120
Get two pieces of cloud brocade for Lady Sourire.

0:03:18.580,0:03:20.400
I am grateful to Your Majesty.

0:03:20.680,0:03:22.120
Can you write?

0:03:22.200,0:03:25.080
Lady Sourire is highly educated and
well versed in poetry and history.

0:03:25.780,0:03:27.520
I have inadequately studied poetry and history.

0:03:27.540,0:03:30.400
But my handwriting may be too inferior
to be of any use to Your Majesty.

0:03:30.680,0:03:32.840
It's good that you can write.

0:03:33.340,0:03:36.020
When you have time,

0:03:37.020,0:03:39.780
come here and copy some sutras for me.

0:03:40.180,0:03:42.280
If Your Majesty is not troubled by my coarseness,

0:03:42.300,0:03:44.880
it will be my great pleasure to serve Your Majesty.

0:03:52.680,0:03:57.040
You've been here one day after another.
Now you have less time to yourself.

0:03:59.160,0:04:02.400
I am honored to copy sutras for Your Majesty.

0:04:08.100,0:04:12.160
Heavy snow broke the tree branches in the courtyard.

0:04:14.220,0:04:16.480
But you were able to write in peace.

0:04:16.800,0:04:19.340
I find that you're very quiet in general.

0:04:20.200,0:04:25.520
My mind wasn't at peace, but copying
sutras for Your Majesty calmed my mind.

0:04:27.220,0:04:31.240
Nothing brings more peace than the words of the Buddha.

0:04:33.600,0:04:34.880
Have you finished?

0:04:35.000,0:04:36.360
Almost.

0:04:54.720,0:04:57.320
Your Majesty also likes sandalwood?

0:04:57.900,0:05:00.300
I burn it as an offering the Buddha.

0:05:01.680,0:05:05.220
It's rarely used in the harem.
How do you recognize the incense?

0:05:05.600,0:05:08.540
I light it for myself sometimes.
It's more calming than benzoin resin.

0:05:08.800,0:05:11.720
That's right. Life has its ups and downs.

0:05:12.340,0:05:15.340
I'm glad you know how to put your mind at peace.

0:05:19.460,0:05:23.340
I said I'm coming tonight. Why did you go to bed early?

0:05:24.020,0:05:27.840
Are you tired from copying the sutras?

0:05:29.480,0:05:31.700
I'm not that delicate.

0:05:33.560,0:05:37.640
I was just feeling cold and sleepy waiting for Your Majesty.

0:05:38.060,0:05:40.420
I lost track of time when I was going through the memorandums.

0:05:40.500,0:05:41.800
It's my fault.

0:05:41.800,0:05:47.380
It's cold and snowy tonight. I thought Your Majesty
would go to Her Majesty's palace since it's close by.

0:05:48.220,0:05:50.580
I just stayed at the Palace of Great Benevolence the day before.

0:05:50.580,0:05:52.820
Why are you telling me to go again?

0:05:53.200,0:05:55.680
It's cold recently and Her Majesty is busy at the year end.

0:05:56.480,0:05:59.300
Her Majesty might be feeling under the weather.

0:05:59.420,0:06:01.580
Your Majesty should spend more time with her.

0:06:02.160,0:06:06.300
When I paid my respects to Her Majesty yesterday, 
I saw her new painting of the winter plums.

0:06:06.540,0:06:07.900
Has Your Majesty seen it yet?

0:06:07.900,0:06:09.680
I haven't.

0:06:09.680,0:06:13.540
I will have lunch with her tomorrow and have a look.

0:06:14.620,0:06:18.400
Her Majesty would put a great deal of effort into a midday meal..

0:06:19.840,0:06:21.640
Perhaps Your Majesty could have dinner with Her Majesty instead?

0:06:21.640,0:06:23.540
Then Your Majesty will able to stay at the Palace of Great Benevolence.

0:06:23.600,0:06:25.960
My Huan Huan is so generous.

0:06:27.880,0:06:29.940
Her Majesty is the mother of the country.

0:06:30.040,0:06:31.900
Your Majesty should spend more time with her.

0:06:32.280,0:06:35.880
That's a very kind request. I will go tomorrow.

0:06:40.240,0:06:43.070
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:06:43.520,0:06:44.960
Rise. Have a seat.

0:06:44.960,0:06:46.620
I thank Your Majesty.

0:06:47.720,0:06:49.160
What is going on today?

0:06:49.260,0:06:52.320
Everyone arrived almost at the same time as if it was planned.

0:06:53.060,0:06:55.400
How coincidental!

0:06:56.160,0:06:58.900
It's very cold lately. Have you been feeling better?

0:06:59.360,0:07:02.280
I feel much better. Thank you for asking.

0:07:06.480,0:07:08.200
Excuse me.

0:07:08.280,0:07:10.100
It was just a cold,

0:07:10.120,0:07:12.660
but it's taking me so long to get over it.

0:07:13.640,0:07:15.360
Did anyone notice?

0:07:15.540,0:07:20.200
Because of the cold, Attendant An's voice is not as beautiful as before.

0:07:20.920,0:07:22.840
Sourire only cares about An.

0:07:22.840,0:07:24.960
You were ignoring me. I'm your sister too.

0:07:25.040,0:07:27.320
Yes, yes you are.

0:07:27.760,0:07:30.040
Everyone is a sister to one another here.

0:07:30.480,0:07:33.640
Sourire, look, I put on some weight again.

0:07:33.840,0:07:36.320
I've outgrown clothes that were just recently made.

0:07:36.520,0:07:39.750
I'm not surprised. Two bowls of porridge
and three sugar buns for breakfast.

0:07:40.160,0:07:41.900
Succulent chicken and duck for lunch.

0:07:41.900,0:07:43.520
Snacks before dinner.

0:07:43.600,0:07:48.640
If I didn't stop you, you would have devoured the entire
pot of ham and pigs feet at dinner.

0:07:48.920,0:07:51.560
Yet you were still hungry and shouting for late night snacks.

0:07:51.560,0:07:55.800
I'm more concerned about your swelling
stomach than the swelling food expenses.

0:07:56.000,0:07:57.840
You are always making fun of me!

0:07:57.960,0:07:59.520
But you are right,

0:07:59.600,0:08:01.120
I must stop eating like this.

0:08:01.280,0:08:04.280
His Majesty said they have to make
new clothes for me every two months.

0:08:04.560,0:08:06.620
I'm either getting taller or bigger.

0:08:07.720,0:08:09.920
I wish I could be like An.

0:08:10.320,0:08:11.960
She's so thin.

0:08:12.720,0:08:14.640
There's nothing wrong with gaining a little weight.

0:08:14.760,0:08:16.360
As long as His Majesty likes it.

0:08:16.560,0:08:19.960
Rather, Attendant An is jealous that you have a healthy appetite.

0:08:20.600,0:08:24.440
Lingrong, you are slim and delicate.

0:08:24.880,0:08:28.800
In addition to your medicine, you should eat more nourishing food.

0:08:31.380,0:08:33.280
I thank Your Majesty.

0:08:33.560,0:08:36.180
I'm not as fortunate as Chun'er.

0:08:36.800,0:08:40.960
She's fortunate to have a good appetite,
and to be cared for.

0:08:42.400,0:08:47.620
Chun'er, Sourire cares about you so much.
She remembers everything you eat.

0:08:51.920,0:08:53.960
All right, take a seat.

0:08:54.900,0:08:56.120
Yes.

0:08:59.560,0:09:01.720
Lady Fuca, are you all right?

0:09:01.960,0:09:04.600
Did you eat something unclean?

0:09:05.720,0:09:08.880
Your Majesty, My Lady didn't eat unclean food.

0:09:08.880,0:09:09.960
My Lady is with child.

0:09:10.040,0:09:11.360
Nonsense.

0:09:11.920,0:09:16.160
Is it true? That's wonderful news!

0:09:17.220,0:09:19.300
We all need to congratulate His Majesty.

0:09:19.300,0:09:22.280
You're with child?
Was it confirmed by an imperial doctor?

0:09:22.680,0:09:24.840
Two doctors have confirmed it.

0:09:25.160,0:09:28.390
I'm not the type who would stoop to anything
to gain His Majesty's favor.

0:09:28.680,0:09:30.680
Yes means yes, no means no.

0:09:30.760,0:09:32.800
Why would I lie about an imperial heir?

0:09:33.120,0:09:35.440
Isn't Companion Shen's example enough?

0:09:35.840,0:09:38.380
Lady Sourire, don't you agree?

0:09:41.480,0:09:43.660
Lady Fuca is truly blessed.

0:09:43.660,0:09:45.580
She had good news very quickly.

0:09:45.800,0:09:49.120
I recall His Majesty has been busy recently.

0:09:49.800,0:09:53.560
His Majesty only visited you every
few months and you got pregnant.

0:09:53.680,0:09:55.340
How blessed you are!

0:09:55.400,0:09:58.700
Indeed, this is a blessing bestowed by Heaven.
[Heaven also refers to an emperor]

0:09:58.800,0:10:00.480
They say it could be a prince.

0:10:00.920,0:10:03.240
Attendant Joie, what do you think?

0:10:03.800,0:10:06.460
Heaven determines whether it is a boy or a girl.

0:10:06.800,0:10:10.560
The fortune of conceiving a prince does not land on everyone.

0:10:10.920,0:10:13.190
All right, a girl is as good as a boy.

0:10:13.560,0:10:17.480
Lady Fuca, you must take care of your health when bearing an imperial heir.

0:10:17.840,0:10:20.140
There mustn't be any oversights.

0:10:20.360,0:10:22.140
I thank your Majesty.

0:10:29.560,0:10:31.640
Noble Lady Sourire!

0:10:33.120,0:10:35.480
There's something my dull-witted mind cannot comprehend.

0:10:35.480,0:10:37.500
I wish to ask you a question.

0:10:37.800,0:10:39.560
I am all ears.

0:10:39.760,0:10:41.820
I am full of pity for you.

0:10:42.180,0:10:44.300
To be honest, you are the most favored

0:10:44.300,0:10:46.720
and the most visited concubine of His Majesty.

0:10:47.340,0:10:50.080
How do you still not have good news for us?

0:10:50.340,0:10:52.400
Now that Lady Fuca is with child,

0:10:52.400,0:10:54.800
His Majesty will pay more attention to her.

0:10:54.900,0:10:59.560
You will have more time to yourself, and 
should improve your reproductive health.

0:11:00.200,0:11:02.200
Lady Fuca bears His Majesty's child.

0:11:02.200,0:11:04.420
Naturally he will spend more time with her.

0:11:05.080,0:11:07.920
Thank you for caring about my health.

0:11:07.960,0:11:10.740
But surely Princess Wenyi's health is your top priority.

0:11:11.260,0:11:14.440
The princess is more precious than gold.
No harm must come to her.

0:11:15.740,0:11:17.980
Thank you.

0:11:22.840,0:11:25.180
Noble Lady Cao has verbally offended Your Highness.

0:11:25.180,0:11:28.340
I entreat Your Highness's forgiveness for her.

0:11:29.800,0:11:31.540
What?

0:11:32.360,0:11:36.480
Lady Cao just said that I am most frequently visited
by His Majesty but not pregnant.

0:11:36.600,0:11:40.300
Her words of mockery also apply to Your Highness.

0:11:40.800,0:11:44.300
Of all His Majesty's concubines,
Your Highness has been visited the most.

0:11:44.300,0:11:47.620
Hence I beg Your Highness's pardon on Cao's behalf.

0:11:49.080,0:11:52.140
What is the big deal about being pregnant?

0:11:53.740,0:11:55.280
Your Highness...

0:11:56.920,0:12:00.080
I will have a son if Heaven blesses me.

0:12:00.660,0:12:04.580
If not, I will have a daughter.

0:12:06.400,0:12:08.660
It's better than not having any.

0:12:08.920,0:12:10.200
I agree with Your Highness.

0:12:10.300,0:12:12.760
His Majesty's favor is not dependent on bearing a heir.

0:12:12.760,0:12:14.960
The belief that a concubine can gain favor by having a child

0:12:14.960,0:12:17.000
is only true if His Majesty cares about the child.

0:12:19.640,0:12:22.600
I bid Your Highness goodbye.

0:12:30.880,0:12:33.200
You are still awake, My Lady.

0:12:33.200,0:12:35.220
It's late. You should rest.

0:12:37.800,0:12:42.320
Lady Fuca got pregnant easily after few times of service.

0:12:42.920,0:12:43.920
But I ...

0:12:44.200,0:12:45.920
haven't have any luck.

0:12:47.520,0:12:50.780
I have to say I'm not as blessed as her.

0:12:51.420,0:12:52.840
How come?

0:12:52.880,0:12:55.300
My Lady, you have Heaven's great blessing.

0:12:55.480,0:12:57.520
Having good news is just a matter of time.

0:12:57.820,0:13:00.380
All you need to do is wait patiently.

0:13:01.060,0:13:06.800
Today, the palace guards told me that
there is a plague spreading in the city.

0:13:07.360,0:13:09.940
It's possible that it will affect the palace.

0:13:10.700,0:13:12.920
You must take extra caution, My Lady.

0:13:15.300,0:13:17.220
Have a good rest.

0:13:20.360,0:13:24.600
I asked Songzhi to send some mountain yam cakes to Lady Fuca.

0:13:24.940,0:13:28.160
But she said she was pregnant and couldn't stand up to thank me.

0:13:28.560,0:13:29.880
How dare she!

0:13:30.600,0:13:35.020
Lady Fuca was brash, but it doesn't mean
she disrespects Your Highness.

0:13:35.500,0:13:37.840
She became so full of herself right after she conceived!

0:13:38.160,0:13:41.780
When she gives birth her arrogance over her increased status will be sky-high!

0:13:42.520,0:13:45.560
Not necessarily. Concort Astuce [Third Prince's mother] is an example.

0:13:46.080,0:13:52.040
Lady Fuca is young and pretty. Her favor from
His Majesty will outlast the older concubines.

0:13:53.240,0:13:54.540
Indeed.

0:13:54.960,0:13:57.440
It won't be too much of a concern if she has a princess.

0:13:57.720,0:13:59.740
But if she gives birth to a prince ...

0:13:59.920,0:14:02.240
It's been a long time since the last prince was born ...

0:14:02.280,0:14:04.200
His Majesty would rejoice greatly ...

0:14:04.440,0:14:07.960
I recall His Majesty only visited you one time this month.

0:14:08.700,0:14:10.820
Now that Lady Fuca is pregnant,

0:14:10.820,0:14:12.660
I'm afraid you'll go from one to zero.

0:14:14.080,0:14:17.740
I only wish for Wenyi to have good health and a peaceful life.

0:14:18.140,0:14:21.660
You can tolerate others, but they might not tolerate you.

0:14:22.160,0:14:25.500
Fortunately, Lady Fuca is not the blessed kind.

0:14:25.840,0:14:28.400
A plague broke out in the city when she got pregnant.

0:14:28.700,0:14:31.040
His Majesty is very concerned about it.

0:14:31.940,0:14:34.940
Your Highness, the plague has reached the palace.

0:14:35.300,0:14:37.020
What?

0:14:43.200,0:14:46.260
Have you distributed dried mugwort to each palace?

0:14:46.540,0:14:48.720
Yes, Your Majesty. We did it overnight.

0:14:49.180,0:14:50.940
Lady Fuca is pregnant.

0:14:50.940,0:14:52.940
Send extra to her palace.

0:14:53.520,0:14:56.540
The Palace of Earthly Honor was the first
to report a carrier of the plague.

0:14:56.540,0:14:58.580
Her palace must be completely cleansed.

0:14:58.580,0:15:02.300
Burn mugwort leaves in her palace to dispel the disease

0:15:02.300,0:15:05.000
every dawn, noon, and dusk.

0:15:05.420,0:15:09.300
In addition, the Imperial Infirmary must prepare medicinal herbs

0:15:09.380,0:15:12.380
for the maids in every palace to make sachets tonight.

0:15:12.380,0:15:15.020
Everyone needs to wear the sachets and put them in their rooms.

0:15:15.260,0:15:16.440
Yes.

0:15:16.560,0:15:17.940
- Dr Zhang.
- Yes.

0:15:18.060,0:15:20.240
You are the head of the Imperial Infirmary.

0:15:20.240,0:15:23.540
What's your understanding of the plague?

0:15:23.720,0:15:26.540
This disease is caused by an external pathogen.

0:15:26.540,0:15:29.240
It starts with a fever and headache,

0:15:29.240,0:15:31.920
and then progresses into severe blood stasis.

0:15:32.120,0:15:33.980
One sick person will infect the entire chamber,

0:15:33.980,0:15:35.900
and one chamber, the entire palace.

0:15:36.000,0:15:39.960
It is better to take preventive measures
as early as possible before it becomes prevalent.

0:15:40.120,0:15:41.900
Is it that serious?

0:15:41.900,0:15:44.260
I dare not make an overstatement before Your Majesty.

0:15:44.580,0:15:47.380
A servant in the harem has already contracted the plague.

0:15:47.380,0:15:49.500
It's coming aggressively from the city!

0:15:49.640,0:15:52.100
The Imperial Infirmary will take early precautions.

0:15:52.560,0:15:57.160
I request Your Majesty to inform the harem
to avoid making unnecessary trips and visits.

0:15:58.000,0:16:01.320
The palace is already in panic after
hearing about the presence of the plague.

0:16:01.420,0:16:04.300
They will strictly obey your instructions, Dr Zhang.

0:16:04.780,0:16:07.700
I trust the Imperial Infirmary will work hard on it.

0:16:08.040,0:16:09.540
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:16:10.220,0:16:13.140
Your Highness, the servant Xiao-Dezi
in our palace contracted the plague.

0:16:13.140,0:16:16.180
The Household Department is going to move him out.

0:16:16.800,0:16:18.500
Immediately!

0:16:18.500,0:16:21.300
Burn everything he has used and worn.

0:16:21.580,0:16:24.300
Smash his pots and cups.

0:16:24.800,0:16:26.940
Scatter lime in his room to dispel bad fortune.

0:16:27.140,0:16:30.400
Your Highness need not worry.
I have already told the servants to do it.

0:16:30.780,0:16:32.980
How can I not worry?

0:16:37.600,0:16:40.100
Peace to Your Highness.

0:16:45.160,0:16:47.960
Your Highness, Her Majesty said that

0:16:47.960,0:16:50.200
the plague has emerged in the palace,

0:16:50.200,0:16:51.740
which requires Your Highness’s assistance.

0:16:51.780,0:16:54.260
Boiling liquor [a disinfectant] has been doused in the Eastern Six Palaces.

0:16:54.260,0:16:56.040
And mugwort leaves are being burned.

0:16:56.040,0:16:58.680
The Western six palaces are entrusted to Your Highness.

0:16:59.520,0:17:01.060
All right.

0:17:01.400,0:17:04.600
Her Majesty also mentioned that although the
Palace of Universal Happiness has fewer occupants,

0:17:04.860,0:17:08.240
Companion Shen’s Chamber of Chrysanthemums
must be opened to burn mugwort leaves.

0:17:08.420,0:17:11.480
Not a palace in the harem should be overlooked.

0:17:12.260,0:17:16.040
Tell Her Majesty I will do it properly.

0:17:16.740,0:17:18.580
Allow me to take my leave

0:17:25.060,0:17:26.540
Liu Ben escaped.

0:17:26.760,0:17:28.820
Shen still remains a menace to me.

0:17:29.900,0:17:31.640
But if Companion Shen is dead ...

0:17:31.780,0:17:34.300
the dead tell no tales even if Liu Ben is caught.

0:17:34.620,0:17:37.100
We failed in getting Shen Meizhuang the death penalty.

0:17:37.680,0:17:39.320
She got very lucky.

0:17:40.220,0:17:43.460
Now we shall let her perish.

0:17:45.120,0:17:48.000
Is there any thing in Xiao-Dezi’s room of use to us?

0:17:48.260,0:17:49.360
Err ...

0:17:49.360,0:17:52.420
There is a tea set that he has been using.

0:17:52.940,0:17:58.180
If it was unknowingly used for tea,
the person would definitely be infected.

0:17:58.680,0:18:02.820
It’s a waste to smash a nice tea set.

0:18:03.920,0:18:06.340
Send it to the Chamber of Chrysanthemums.

0:18:06.660,0:18:08.440
Understood.

0:18:15.720,0:18:17.360
His Majesty cares for you, My Lady,

0:18:17.360,0:18:19.340
and ordered us to clean up your chamber.

0:18:19.500,0:18:21.960
We hope to protect you from the plague, My Lady.

0:18:22.520,0:18:25.020
I seek your forgiveness for any inconveniences.

0:18:25.920,0:18:28.200
Mind your own work and I will I fend for myself .

0:18:28.540,0:18:29.840
There is no inconvenience.

0:18:29.900,0:18:31.340
Yes, My Lady.

0:18:32.400,0:18:34.480
Scatter some liquor outside.

0:18:35.120,0:18:36.580
Come in.

0:18:43.060,0:18:47.180
My Lady, the Household Department sends you a new tea set

0:18:47.460,0:18:50.580
since your utensils are not in good condition.

0:18:51.060,0:18:53.440
The tea has been made for you, My Lady.

0:18:53.940,0:18:55.740
Thank you.

0:18:56.520,0:18:57.860
My Lady,

0:18:57.860,0:19:00.020
We have almost finished the work outside.

0:19:00.020,0:19:03.520
I have to go to the other palaces if you allow me.

0:19:06.400,0:19:08.800
I bid you goodbye, My Lady.

0:19:10.040,0:19:11.980
You have been coughing lately.

0:19:11.980,0:19:14.020
Make sure you take extra care of yourself.

0:19:14.180,0:19:15.980
Thank you.

0:19:16.760,0:19:18.500
Thank you, My Lady.

0:19:18.500,0:19:22.060
We are burning mugwort leaves three times a day as required.

0:19:23.480,0:19:26.320
The Imperial Infirmary sent some medical sachets .

0:19:26.320,0:19:30.660
I took some more for you since you've been feeling unwell.

0:19:32.920,0:19:37.120
The Palace of Pearl Jade is well provided for
since you and Attendant Chun live there.

0:19:37.480,0:19:38.720
What are these ?

0:19:38.740,0:19:43.120
The Imperial Infirmary sent some Bai Zhu root
to be burned with the mugwort.

0:19:43.500,0:19:45.080
This basket is for the Palace of Prolonging Happiness.

0:19:45.080,0:19:47.660
Oh, put them all in my chamber.

0:19:47.880,0:19:49.940
This is for everyone in the Palace of Prolonging Happiness.

0:19:49.940,0:19:52.120
Why didn't Attendant An receive any?

0:19:53.500,0:19:54.980
I beg your pardon, Lady Fuca.

0:19:54.980,0:19:57.580
You must give some to Attendant An.

0:19:57.900,0:20:01.100
Attendant An is strong and healthy.
She doesn't need this.

0:20:01.480,0:20:04.900
I am with His Majesty's child.
I need to be treated with more care.

0:20:05.220,0:20:09.120
I will surely give priority to Attendant An when she is pregnant.

0:20:10.080,0:20:12.400
Lady Fuca, you and your child's health matter.

0:20:12.400,0:20:14.080
So does Attendant An's.

0:20:14.480,0:20:17.180
The Imperial Infirmary will keep sending the herbs.

0:20:17.340,0:20:20.040
Why would you have all of them to yourself?

0:20:20.680,0:20:24.020
Ah I see, in the presence of Lady Sourire,

0:20:24.260,0:20:27.920
Attendant An finds the courage to argue for things.

0:20:29.860,0:20:32.360
Fuca, you misunderstood. I didn't intend to.

0:20:32.560,0:20:34.180
Attendant An has a good temper.

0:20:34.180,0:20:36.180
But I have to say this for her.

0:20:36.400,0:20:38.960
What happens in my palace is what I say.

0:20:39.180,0:20:41.840
You are welcome to tell His Majesty if you disagree.

0:20:42.420,0:20:46.420
I believe His Majesty will give priority to an imperial heir.

0:20:46.880,0:20:50.820
You don't need to involve His Majesty to make sense of this.

0:20:52.100,0:20:54.900
If you use all the Bai Zhu root,

0:20:55.100,0:20:59.500
and Attendant An then contracts the disease, won't your own palace be at more risk?

0:20:59.780,0:21:01.460
Are you cursing me ?

0:21:01.800,0:21:04.080
You will be in trouble when I tell His Majesty.

0:21:04.360,0:21:07.020
It's up to you whether you should tell His Majesty.

0:21:07.560,0:21:12.120
I'm afraid His Majesty will agree that
you are not thinking of the greater good.

0:21:12.620,0:21:14.300
I'm not going to listen to you.

0:21:14.400,0:21:15.200
Move them in.

0:21:15.800,0:21:16.600
And shut the door

0:21:22.560,0:21:25.460
Sourire, don't waste your breath and cause yourself trouble.

0:21:25.600,0:21:27.040
I know it was pointless.

0:21:27.040,0:21:30.360
But if I don't speak up for you,
she will do this time after time.

0:21:30.880,0:21:33.800
That will upset you again and again.

0:21:34.180,0:21:35.200
Let's go back to the room.

0:21:36.300,0:21:38.460
I will ask the Imperial Infirmary for some Bai Zhu.

0:21:38.780,0:21:40.560
It is not that easy.

0:21:40.560,0:21:43.640
I would not contend with her if it was easily available.

0:21:45.260,0:21:46.960
Let's go.

