0:22:02.820,0:22:04.460
How many people died today?

0:22:04.560,0:22:05.880
Already two this morning.

0:22:06.600,0:22:08.520
The plague is spreading ferociously.

0:22:08.840,0:22:11.260
Even the Imperial Infirmary hasn't a clue what to do.

0:22:11.260,0:22:13.480
His Majesty, Her Majesty, Consort Fleur, and Consort Astuce,

0:22:13.480,0:22:16.040
have been praying for two days in the Baohua Hall.

0:22:17.740,0:22:19.780
The plague has spread all over the city.

0:22:20.180,0:22:22.720
The imperial doctors are "a cup of water on a burning carriage".

0:22:22.720,0:22:25.800
His Majesty has lost weight after a few days of anxiety.

0:22:27.840,0:22:30.040
Such a pungent smell.

0:22:30.180,0:22:35.100
It is. The maids have been boiling
vinegar to prevent the spread of the plague.

0:22:35.860,0:22:37.700
It makes the palace smell unpleasant.

0:22:37.800,0:22:40.900
I have got used to the smell.

0:22:44.420,0:22:45.980
My Lady, terrible news!

0:22:46.460,0:22:48.660
Inform My Lady calmly.

0:22:49.220,0:22:52.320
The Palace of Universal Happiness reported that
Lady Meizhuang contracted the plague.

0:22:54.260,0:22:56.920
My Lady, don't go!

0:22:58.480,0:22:59.820
How did this happen?

0:22:59.940,0:23:02.640
Take it easy, Sourire. Have a seat.

0:23:06.240,0:23:09.000
She was all right yesterday.

0:23:10.060,0:23:13.820
But this morning, Orchid reported that
she vomited all that she ate

0:23:14.020,0:23:15.740
and developed a high fever.

0:23:15.940,0:23:18.200
And she began to talk deliriously since noon.

0:23:18.540,0:23:20.980
What about the imperial doctors? Did they come?

0:23:21.100,0:23:22.540
Forget about the doctors.

0:23:22.540,0:23:24.820
Companion Shen has long been neglected in her confinement.

0:23:24.820,0:23:26.640
The plague is very contagious.

0:23:26.640,0:23:28.160
Who dares to go?

0:23:28.600,0:23:30.460
I've sent for doctors a few times.

0:23:30.680,0:23:32.500
But no one visited.

0:23:33.320,0:23:35.680
Sourire, what should we do?

0:23:35.880,0:23:37.580
I've tried my best.

0:23:37.840,0:23:42.260
I wanted to ask His Majesty for help,
but he has been at court all morning.

0:23:42.560,0:23:44.580
The Empress Dowager, the Empress, and the consorts

0:23:44.700,0:23:46.320
are all praying in the Baohua Hall.

0:23:46.800,0:23:49.480
There's no one who can order the doctors to come.

0:23:52.840,0:23:54.380
I will go see her.

0:23:54.700,0:23:56.920
- You mustn't go, My Lady.
- Don't go, My Lady.

0:23:56.920,0:23:59.580
Sourire, it's dangerous to go into her chamber.

0:24:00.120,0:24:02.020
The disease is infectious.

0:24:02.020,0:24:04.380
I can't decide for her before I see her.

0:24:04.860,0:24:05.940
My Lady...

0:24:06.240,0:24:07.680
My Lady!

0:24:08.440,0:24:10.920
My Lady, I know you are worried about Lady Meizhuang.

0:24:10.960,0:24:12.680
But you must also care for yourself.

0:24:12.680,0:24:13.420
Exactly.

0:24:13.500,0:24:15.080
You should just look from behind the door.

0:24:15.080,0:24:16.780
I'm going in for one glance. Just one quick look.

0:24:16.780,0:24:18.360
My Lady, don't.

0:24:18.380,0:24:20.260
Lady Meizhuang is already infected.

0:24:20.260,0:24:21.580
You have to protect yourself.

0:24:21.580,0:24:22.800
Just one glance.

0:24:22.800,0:24:25.880
Otherwise there would be no one
to speak for Lady Meizhuang.

0:24:34.320,0:24:37.420
Please look after her, Madam.

0:24:42.040,0:24:43.220
Mr Su.

0:24:43.380,0:24:45.560
I hope you can understand, My Lady.

0:24:45.940,0:24:47.820
The plague is rampant in the city.

0:24:47.840,0:24:51.040
His Majesty is anxious and discussing it with his ministers.

0:24:51.300,0:24:53.560
His Majesty can't spare a minute right now.

0:24:53.700,0:24:56.060
How much longer will the discussions take?

0:24:56.120,0:24:59.300
It's a serious matter. I can't speculate on that.

0:24:59.500,0:25:02.540
If it is very urgent, My Lady,
you should go see the Empress first.

0:25:02.780,0:25:04.200
I'm afraid I should not.

0:25:04.280,0:25:07.500
I can't see Her Majesty without His Majesty's permission.

0:25:08.220,0:25:10.060
Is this about Companion Shen?

0:25:11.020,0:25:13.180
You'd better not, My Lady.

0:25:13.360,0:25:15.560
If you would listen to me, My Lady,

0:25:15.600,0:25:18.880
His Majesty has been distressed over the plague.

0:25:19.180,0:25:23.300
You should not mention Companion Shen
and add to His Majesty's stress.

0:25:24.180,0:25:25.900
You should consider other solutions.

0:25:26.360,0:25:28.240
Thank you, sir.

0:25:28.640,0:25:31.480
But please inform His Majesty when you have a chance.

0:25:31.760,0:25:33.220
Yes, My Lady.

0:25:49.240,0:25:52.100
Wen Shichu bows before Lady Sourire.

0:25:53.780,0:25:55.400
Please rise, Dr Wen.

0:25:55.640,0:25:57.140
Thank you, My Lady.

0:25:57.140,0:25:58.800
May I speak to you privately?

0:26:04.240,0:26:07.760
Dr Wen, are you still occupied with the treatment of the plague?

0:26:07.920,0:26:09.060
I am.

0:26:09.060,0:26:12.600
Would you be willing to help me if I ask for a favor?

0:26:13.700,0:26:15.580
To be frank with you, sir,

0:26:15.580,0:26:17.460
helping me will not bring you any recognition,

0:26:17.540,0:26:20.040
and may result in serious punishment if others find out.

0:26:20.560,0:26:24.200
But my heart will never rest easy if I don't ask.

0:26:25.020,0:26:29.920
My Lady, will it ease your mind if I am willing to do it?

0:26:31.120,0:26:34.280
If you help me, sir, my mind will be at peace.

0:26:35.660,0:26:38.900
For that, My Lady, I will do everything I can.

0:26:40.060,0:26:41.960
I'm at your disposal.

0:26:43.600,0:26:47.100
Companion Shen contracted the plague in the Chamber of Chrysanthemums.

0:26:47.100,0:26:48.500
Her life is at stake.

0:26:48.800,0:26:51.240
I'm asking you to help her.

0:26:51.300,0:26:52.000
But ...

0:26:54.400,0:26:55.880
she is a concubine in solitary confinement.

0:26:57.820,0:27:01.760
No matter who she is, I will do what you ask me to

0:27:02.640,0:27:04.840
if that will bring peace to your mind.

0:27:05.940,0:27:07.940
Thank you, Dr Wen.

0:27:09.280,0:27:12.460
Allow me to take my leave, My Lady.

0:27:15.220,0:27:16.880
Dr Wen.

0:27:20.640,0:27:22.660
Please take care.

0:27:30.680,0:27:32.200
Five maces of Dong'e ejiao...

0:27:32.300,0:27:35.440
His Majesty didn't even have
the appetite to eat because of the plague.

0:27:35.760,0:27:37.880
You must find the cure without delay!

0:27:38.000,0:27:39.440
Yes, Your Highness.

0:27:40.100,0:27:41.580
Your Highness must be patient.

0:27:41.820,0:27:43.360
We have never had a prescription for an epidemic like this.

0:27:43.440,0:27:45.780
We are like "the blind men and an elephant" - groping slowly.

0:27:46.000,0:27:47.420
Slowly?

0:27:47.600,0:27:49.500
I can't bear to see His Majesty so anxious.

0:27:49.980,0:27:51.440
We are trying our best.

0:27:51.880,0:27:54.320
Are you? You've been searching the books for days.

0:27:54.460,0:27:55.980
What have you found?

0:27:56.200,0:27:57.880
I might as well read this myself!

0:27:58.080,0:28:00.440
Your Highness has stayed up for nights.

0:28:00.540,0:28:04.160
We would be held responsible should Your Highness feel unwell.

0:28:08.080,0:28:10.660
Dr.Wen, you should go rest.

0:28:12.240,0:28:15.480
The prescription is almost completed.

0:28:16.440,0:28:22.270
Sir, you have been working hard day and night on the plague formula.

0:28:23.000,0:28:25.280
I have to be faithful to a promise.

0:28:25.820,0:28:27.960
Work is not hard but duty.

0:28:28.380,0:28:29.560
Yes.

0:28:33.680,0:28:36.460
Dr. Wen is still here. You have been working hard.

0:28:37.400,0:28:38.900
Dr. Jiang.

0:28:39.420,0:28:42.720
Dr. Wen, you have to take care of the concubines during the day,

0:28:43.340,0:28:46.400
and pursue the remedy for the plague at night.

0:28:47.000,0:28:48.840
You must be exhausted.

0:28:49.380,0:28:51.660
Did you make any progress on the prescription?

0:28:52.020,0:28:53.300
Not yet.

0:28:53.300,0:28:55.660
But I will do my best.

0:28:55.960,0:28:57.700
I’ll go now since you’re busy.

0:28:58.160,0:29:00.300
After Lady Meizhuang was infected with the plague,

0:29:00.320,0:29:03.860
the guards were afraid to get close to her and thus slacking.

0:29:04.560,0:29:08.560
I have secretly sent Dr. Wen into her chamber.

0:29:09.240,0:29:11.260
How are Lunar and Stellar?

0:29:11.260,0:29:13.540
They are very conscientious ...

0:29:13.720,0:29:18.100
Lady Meizhuang is not improving because Dr. Wen is treating her in secret,

0:29:18.500,0:29:25.300
so he can't order all the herbs or the nourishing food she needs to get well.

0:29:25.300,0:29:28.720
But I'm afraid that's all we can do for now.

0:29:29.660,0:29:31.740
Yes, My Lady.

0:29:32.520,0:29:36.020
Congratulation, My Lady! Your wish came true.

0:29:37.900,0:29:39.000
Su Peisheng.

0:29:39.000,0:29:40.000
Your Majesty.

0:29:40.040,0:29:42.440
How serious is the plague in the palace now?

0:29:42.600,0:29:46.820
Your Majesty, the servants died one after another.

0:29:47.200,0:29:49.440
The palace is in a panic.

0:29:49.640,0:29:52.800
If so, it must be much worse outside the palace.

0:29:53.100,0:29:57.500
Yes, I heard that all the wealthy families
tried to escape town

0:29:57.960,0:30:01.900
only to see the suburbs full of infected citizens.

0:30:02.240,0:30:04.160
So they were frightened and came back.

0:30:04.280,0:30:07.580
I’ve heard that the city itself isn't the most affected area.

0:30:08.040,0:30:10.160
The village in Yongping is more afflicted.

0:30:10.240,0:30:16.640
Yes, the villagers were locked up in quarantine
as soon as they showed symptoms of the plague.

0:30:17.160,0:30:22.140
The detainees had no way out but death.

0:30:25.440,0:30:28.220
Lady Sourire requests an audience with Your Majesty.

0:30:28.220,0:30:29.960
At this time of the night?

0:30:29.960,0:30:31.740
It must be something urgent, Your Majesty.

0:30:32.020,0:30:34.080
- Show her in.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

0:30:42.180,0:30:43.800
Peace to Lady Sourire.

0:30:44.740,0:30:46.740
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:30:47.860,0:30:50.780
What happened? Is it very urgent?

0:30:52.440,0:30:54.000
You can go now.

0:30:55.020,0:30:56.580
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:31:01.260,0:31:03.100
Go ahead.

0:31:06.560,0:31:08.540
Xiao-Yunzi.

0:31:14.160,0:31:16.340
You don't raise your head before His Majesty?

0:31:17.960,0:31:21.220
Liu Ben bows in respect before Your Majesty.

0:31:21.480,0:31:23.280
Why are you here?

0:31:23.600,0:31:27.000
I never believed that Companion Shen
would feign pregnancy to gain favor.

0:31:27.240,0:31:29.320
So I secretly began to search for Liu Ben.

0:31:29.320,0:31:31.920
They finally found him at
the border of Yongzhou, Hunan Province.

0:31:32.500,0:31:34.420
The maid Poria was flogged to death.

0:31:34.520,0:31:36.760
But Liu Ben was taking care of Companion Shen all along.

0:31:36.800,0:31:39.080
He is the only one who knows exactly what happened to Shen.

0:31:41.800,0:31:44.260
I won’t force confession under torture.

0:31:44.600,0:31:47.600
But if you dare to tell a word of untruth,

0:31:48.440,0:31:51.320
I will make you suffer more than death.

0:31:52.800,0:31:57.020
I heard that when he was found, he was
disguised as a beggar to avoid being discovered.

0:31:57.880,0:32:00.620
Dr Liu, you don't have to tell us anything.

0:32:01.200,0:32:05.000
But if you do so, I will send you out of the palace right away.

0:32:05.800,0:32:09.440
I bet they will cut off your head
before you can leave Beijing.

0:32:09.620,0:32:14.300
If you still choose not to tell the truth,
you are digging your own grave.

0:32:15.720,0:32:18.320
Your Majesty, Lady Meizhuang was never pregnant.

0:32:19.700,0:32:20.880
That I know.

0:32:20.880,0:32:24.140
But Lady Meizhuang didn't know that herself.

0:32:24.840,0:32:28.140
When she was in "prenatal care",
her menstruation had stopped.

0:32:28.680,0:32:33.260
And her symptoms -- dizziness and
vomiting - were caused by medication, not pregnancy.

0:32:33.960,0:32:39.960
But before I took her pulse, I was ordered
to diagnose her with pregnancy regardless.

0:32:40.480,0:32:42.840
You were ordered? By whom?

0:32:43.280,0:32:44.440
By …

0:32:45.320,0:32:48.760
She is going to kill you.
Why are you hesitant to say her name?

0:32:49.920,0:32:52.480
Consort Fleur. It was Consort Fleur.

0:32:55.240,0:32:57.320
If you have told a single word of untruth ...

0:32:57.840,0:32:59.800
I dare not, Your Majesty, I dare not.

0:32:59.800,0:33:01.700
I know I have committed a capital offense.

0:33:02.040,0:33:04.360
Consort Fleur gave me a sum of money,

0:33:04.400,0:33:06.520
and told me to leave the Summer Palace
at once to avoid trouble.

0:33:06.640,0:33:09.880
She assured me that I would be
aided when I got back to the city.

0:33:09.960,0:33:12.780
But as soon as I entered the city,
there were killers chasing after me all the way.

0:33:13.120,0:33:16.360
I was running around for life like a homeless dog.

0:33:17.960,0:33:20.600
Xiao-Yunzi, take him out and keep him under close watch.

0:33:20.800,0:33:22.340
Don't let anything happen.

0:33:22.440,0:33:23.780
Yes, My Lady.

0:33:23.880,0:33:26.020
Come with me.

0:33:29.100,0:33:30.680
May peace be restored in Your Majesty.

0:33:30.680,0:33:35.060
Is it possible that ... he has not told the entire truth?

0:33:35.560,0:33:38.120
There is much doubt over
what happened to Companion Shen.

0:33:38.120,0:33:39.820
But we have no evidence.

0:33:39.960,0:33:43.860
In hindsight, if Shen menstruated a few days before,

0:33:43.860,0:33:48.580
why would she have her stained clothing
discarded right in Your Majesty's presence?

0:33:49.520,0:33:53.880
Also, Companion Shen mentioned that Dr. Jiang
had given her a prescription to help with pregnancy.

0:33:54.360,0:33:56.620
But it went missing right when we were looking for it.

0:33:56.680,0:33:58.700
If the prescription never existed,

0:33:58.700,0:34:01.040
wouldn't it have been very stupid of Shen to mention it?

0:34:02.340,0:34:04.100
I’m afraid Your Majesty has the same doubts.

0:34:04.100,0:34:06.180
I saw that prescription before.

0:34:06.400,0:34:09.600
It didn't seem improper to me.

0:34:13.640,0:34:16.040
Consort Fleur.

0:34:17.020,0:34:19.100
Very well.

0:34:19.480,0:34:24.600
That prescription to prove Meizhuang's
innocence was probably stolen.

0:34:25.140,0:34:27.540
That maid called Poria...

0:34:27.800,0:34:29.900
She must be involved in this.

0:34:30.160,0:34:33.660
I flogged Poria to death that day out of unrestrained rage.

0:34:34.240,0:34:39.040
If only I interrogated her instead.

0:34:39.660,0:34:41.320
Your Majesty's is not to blame.

0:34:41.320,0:34:45.700
Poria must have been determined to ruin Companion Shen
since she dared to defame her.

0:34:46.240,0:34:48.080
But now ...

0:34:49.100,0:34:51.100
What will Your Majesty do?

0:34:51.480,0:34:53.300
I wronged Meizhuang.

0:34:53.860,0:34:56.600
I will let her out and restore her title.

0:34:56.860,0:34:58.220
I'm afraid it's too late.

0:34:58.220,0:34:59.860
Did she ...

0:35:00.440,0:35:02.880
No, Meizhuang didn't have any suicidal thoughts.

0:35:02.880,0:35:05.920
But contracted the plague due to depression and weakened Qi.

0:35:06.420,0:35:09.820
There's was nothing for her to worry over.

0:35:10.340,0:35:14.060
Confinement may have been the only punishment imposed.

0:35:14.760,0:35:20.460
But because she fell from grace,
all the servants in the palace disdain her.

0:35:22.080,0:35:26.640
I will send imperial doctors to treat Lady Vertu immediately.

0:35:27.420,0:35:30.060
I won't let anything happen to her.

0:35:32.680,0:35:35.260
I beg Your Majesty's forgiveness for my offence.

0:35:35.260,0:35:40.540
When I saw she was seriously ill,
I secretly asked an imperial doctor to take care of her.

0:35:40.880,0:35:41.900
You did?

0:35:41.900,0:35:43.600
I seek Your Majesty's pardon.

0:35:43.960,0:35:46.920
Had you not risked your life to safe hers,

0:35:47.840,0:35:51.460
I would have been in eternal regret for Lady Vertu.

0:35:51.660,0:35:53.460
Your Majesty did nothing wrong.

0:35:53.460,0:35:56.040
The sly evildoer "clouded your wisdom eyes".

0:36:03.960,0:36:06.260
Consort Fleur fooled me into this ...

0:36:06.600,0:36:08.380
I won't forgive her.

0:36:10.120,0:36:11.460
Su Peisheng.

0:36:16.100,0:36:17.420
Your Majesty.

0:36:17.420,0:36:19.900
Bring my order to the Imperial Infirmary:

0:36:21.000,0:36:23.680
Jiang Cheng and Jiang Sheng are granted suicide.

0:36:23.780,0:36:27.660
Consort Fleur is deprived of her
honorary name and demoted to Noble Lady.

0:36:30.440,0:36:32.040
Wait.

0:36:33.060,0:36:36.900
Deprived of her honorary name and demoted to Concubine.

0:36:37.700,0:36:42.800
Your Majesty, the deprivation of honorary name is
a greater punishment than demotion.

0:36:43.720,0:36:45.200
What made Your Majesty so upset?

0:36:45.200,0:36:47.240
Go to the Palace of Universal Happiness first ...

0:36:47.240,0:36:50.880
Declare that I have restored Lady Vertu's status and honorary name.

0:36:51.800,0:36:53.480
Her health takes priority.

0:36:53.760,0:36:54.840
Yes.

0:36:54.940,0:36:58.360
But it's very late now.

0:36:58.800,0:37:01.560
If the Household Department delivers Your Majesty's decree now,

0:37:01.560,0:37:03.740
I'm afraid it will disturb the entire harem.

0:37:04.120,0:37:06.120
Then do it tomorrow.

0:37:07.380,0:37:09.520
Act as if nothing happened.

0:37:10.080,0:37:11.120
I understand.

0:37:11.120,0:37:13.600
I will go to the Palace of Universal Happiness now.

0:37:20.640,0:37:22.520
Huan Huan ...

0:37:22.520,0:37:26.140
Did you arrange Liu Ben to ...

0:37:26.760,0:37:27.960
What?

0:37:27.960,0:37:29.820
Nothing.

0:37:31.800,0:37:36.240
Does Your Majesty think I instructed Liu Ben to defame Consort Fleur?

0:37:38.040,0:37:40.720
Does Your Majesty think I'm that kind of person?

0:37:41.700,0:37:43.380
I dare not ...

0:37:44.300,0:37:46.360
I am too proud to do that.

0:37:47.160,0:37:52.160
If I had intended to save Lady Vertu and defame
Consort Fleur, I wouldn't have waited until today.

0:37:53.000,0:37:56.420
I wouldn't have waited until Lady Vertu's life is in peril.

0:38:00.140,0:38:02.460
If Your Majesty distrusts me,

0:38:02.720,0:38:05.040
Mr. Su can't have gotten far.

0:38:05.040,0:38:07.200
Your Majesty can revoke the decree.

0:38:11.060,0:38:12.980
I was being suspicious.

0:38:13.040,0:38:16.800
If I didn't believe you, I wouldn't have punished Consort Fleur.

0:38:16.960,0:38:20.200
If Your Majesty trusts me, Your Majesty wouldn't have asked that.

0:38:20.260,0:38:21.660
Huan Huan.

0:38:27.200,0:38:28.540
I misspoke.

0:38:28.940,0:38:31.400
It's all right. Rise.

0:38:32.920,0:38:35.060
I thank Your Majesty.

0:39:03.880,0:39:09.440
Consort Fleur has always been thorough and attentive in her service.

0:39:11.480,0:39:14.840
I thought she was just domineering sometimes,

0:39:15.680,0:39:20.760
but I'm really disappointed about what she did this time.

0:39:23.060,0:39:24.920
I understand, Your Majesty.

0:39:25.900,0:39:28.620
Great news for the Palace of
Universal Happiness and Lady Vertu.

0:39:28.640,0:39:31.440
His Majesty has lifted Lady Vertu's confinement.

0:39:32.460,0:39:34.740
Her title and rewards remain the same as before.

0:39:34.840,0:39:36.920
I'm grateful to His Majesty.

0:39:39.360,0:39:40.980
Congratulations.

0:39:41.780,0:39:43.180
Thank you, Mr. Su.

0:39:43.180,0:39:45.840
What a joyous moment of vindication!

0:39:46.160,0:39:47.520
Exactly.

0:39:48.000,0:39:52.920
But unfortunately, Lady Vertu cannot
hear the good news for herself.

0:39:55.520,0:39:57.940
Is she still unconscious?

0:40:04.200,0:40:06.700
Dr. Wen, My Lady's fever has broken.

0:40:06.880,0:40:09.080
But she vomited the medicine.

0:40:09.200,0:40:10.560
How much did she vomit?

0:40:10.580,0:40:12.600
About one third.

0:40:14.440,0:40:18.400
But I did follow the prescription for her symptoms.

0:40:18.960,0:40:20.920
Maybe the medicine was too strong.

0:40:20.920,0:40:23.840
I'll try to adjust the dosage.

0:40:28.840,0:40:32.760
Dr. Wen, is Lady Vertu feeling better?

0:40:33.660,0:40:34.860
A little bit.

0:40:35.260,0:40:37.440
But her illness was not promptly reported.

0:40:37.440,0:40:39.600
She is gravely ill and still unconscious.

0:40:40.200,0:40:42.780
Please allow me to some time to figure it out.

0:40:43.560,0:40:45.520
That's very kind of you, sir.

0:40:45.600,0:40:48.820
I heard that you have been here for over a day.

0:40:50.080,0:40:53.600
I will have a guilty conscience if I cannot cure My Lady.

0:40:55.880,0:41:00.800
For your tireless dedication, sir,
I will surely inform His Majesty to reward you.

0:41:02.560,0:41:04.920
My Lady, the plague is rampant in the palace.

0:41:05.120,0:41:07.520
Are we really going to visit Lady Meizhuang?

0:41:08.140,0:41:10.200
His Majesty reinstated Lady Vertu's title.

0:41:10.200,0:41:12.360
I'm afraid she is seriously ill.

0:41:13.320,0:41:17.780
But don't worry, the guards won't let us in.

0:41:18.560,0:41:20.360
We will just send our greetings outside.

0:41:20.520,0:41:21.980
Yes, My Lady.

0:41:23.680,0:41:25.360
Peace to Attendant An.

0:41:25.360,0:41:28.820
Mr. Xia, I'm here to visit Lady Vertu.

0:41:29.160,0:41:30.840
The imperial doctor is busy taking care of her.

0:41:30.920,0:41:32.540
I'm afraid it's not a convenient time, My Lady.

0:41:32.540,0:41:36.360
And since the plague is infectious,
you should stay away from here, My Lady.

0:41:36.680,0:41:39.540
Sir, may I trouble you to inform Lady Vertu that I visited?

0:41:39.760,0:41:41.680
I will, My Lady.

0:41:41.880,0:41:46.640
Do you know ... why His Majesty
reinstated Lady Vertu so suddenly?

0:41:47.080,0:41:49.560
Didn't Lady Sourire tell you, My Lady?

0:41:49.600,0:41:51.560
The culprit, Liu Ben was captured.

0:41:51.880,0:41:52.900
Really?

0:41:52.920,0:41:55.020
You don't have to believe me, My Lady.

0:41:56.080,0:41:57.560
You are His Majesty's direct servant.

0:41:57.560,0:41:59.080
I believe you.

0:41:59.640,0:42:03.400
The news was unexpected.
What a wonderful surprise!

0:42:04.040,0:42:06.320
Exactly, My Lady.

0:42:06.560,0:42:09.680
Someone will be in great trouble
now that Liu Ben has been caught.

0:42:13.480,0:42:14.580
Who?

0:42:14.580,0:42:15.780
I can't tell you now

0:42:15.840,0:42:18.440
because it would cause chaos in the palace.

